# 🧠 RAG Pipeline — Document Intelligence System

Ask questions about any document using AI. Upload a PDF, get instant answers powered by semantic search and LLMs.

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.12-blue)
![FastAPI](https://img.shields.io/badge/FastAPI-0.115-green)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow)

---

## 🚀 What it does

Upload any PDF → Ask questions → Get accurate AI-powered answers

Built with a full MLOps stack including evaluation, monitoring, caching, and automated pipelines.

---

## 🏗️ Architecture
```
PDF / Document
      ↓
Ingestion → Chunking → Embeddings (HuggingFace E5)
      ↓
Qdrant Vector DB
      ↓
Semantic Search + Reranking
      ↓
Groq LLM (Llama 3.1)
      ↓
Answer
```

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Tool |
|-------|------|
| Framework | LangChain |
| Vector DB | Qdrant |
| Embeddings | HuggingFace E5 |
| LLM | Groq (Llama 3.1) |
| Cache | Redis |
| Evaluation | RAGAS |
| Experiment Tracking | MLflow |
| Monitoring | Grafana + Prometheus |
| Orchestration | Apache Airflow |
| API | FastAPI |
| UI | Streamlit |
| CI/CD | GitHub Actions |
| Containerization | Docker |

---

## 📦 Project Structure
```
rag-pipeline/
├── ingestion/        # document loaders (PDF, web, SQL)
├── chunking/         # semantic text splitting
├── embeddings/       # HuggingFace embedding models
├── retrieval/        # vector search + reranking
├── generation/       # LLM answer generation
├── evaluation/       # RAGAS quality scoring
├── cache/            # Redis caching layer
├── tracking/         # MLflow experiment logging
├── orchestration/    # Airflow DAGs + pipeline
├── api/              # FastAPI endpoints
├── app.py            # Streamlit UI
└── tests/            # unit + integration tests
```

