REDIS_HOST=localhost
MLFLOW_TRACKING_URI=http://localhost:5000
RAG_API_KEY=your_secret_key
```

---

## 📊 Evaluation

Every query is evaluated using RAGAS metrics:

| Metric | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| Faithfulness | Is the answer grounded in retrieved chunks? |
| Answer Relevancy | Does it actually answer the question? |
| Context Recall | Were the right chunks retrieved? |

